General.Name: Top Shelf International Holdings
General.Description: Top Shelf International Holdings Ltd engages in the production, marketing, and selling of NED Australian Whisky and Grainshaker Hand Made Vodka spirit products in Australia. It also provides canning, bottling, and contract packaging services to third party beverage manufacturers; and produces Australian agave spirit. The company was incorporated in 2013 and is headquartered in Campbellfield, Australia.
